headline: Could Investing $10,000 in Realty Income Make You a Millionaire?
summary: Realty Income is a large and high-yield net lease REIT.  If you invested $10,000 in Realty Income (NYSE: O) at the turn of the last century, it would be worth around $56,000 today.  The truth is, Realty Income has outperformed the S&P 500 index (SNPINDEX: ^GSPC) over that span.
